snippet.title: Namachuukei 68 (Sharp X68000) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Uploading a higher-quality recording of Namachuukei 68 (Live Broadcast 68), a 1991 baseball game by Konami for the Sharp X68000, a Japanese computer. 

I think this is a really gorgeous game, and interesting for predating Konami's Power Pros series while using some similar gameplay. The fantastic music was done by the future Dark Souls sound designer Yuji Takenouchi. 

For more on the game and how to play it today, check out 30-30.club here: https://30-30.club/wiki/namachuukei-68/

Home run timestamps: 
31:07

Do not miss the sick postgame animations and music from 45:08 on.
